wiki.summary: Lucky Girl Syndrome is a song by ILLIT. It is the fourth and final track on their debut album 'SUPER REAL ME' and was released on March 25, 2024. Lucky Girl Syndrome, with its playful whistle theme line, is a dance pop song that immediately catches the listener's ears. The light rhythm and repeated guitar phrases in the intro convey the song's quirky charm, while the heavy rhythm and refreshing melody that emerges from the hook enrich the overall composition of the song. Read more on Last.fm.
wiki.content: Lucky Girl Syndrome is a song by ILLIT. It is the fourth and final track on their debut album 'SUPER REAL ME' and was released on March 25, 2024. Lucky Girl Syndrome, with its playful whistle theme line, is a dance pop song that immediately catches the listener's ears. The light rhythm and repeated guitar phrases in the intro convey the song's quirky charm, while the heavy rhythm and refreshing melody that emerges from the hook enrich the overall composition of the song. You can feel ILLIT’s unique positive power by singing “I’m Lucky” to small things such as “perfect weather” and “just the right playlist. Read more on Last.fm.
